{
  "version": 1,
  "cues": [
    {
      "start": 1,
      "end": 5.993,
      "text": "来做一个有趣的实验。我们会把一个包含约 1",
      "words": [
        { "start": 1, "end": 3.497, "char": [0, 19] },
        { "start": 3.497, "end": 5.993, "char": [20, 21] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 5.993,
      "end": 10.986,
      "text": "GB 数据的",
      "words": [
        { "start": 5.993, "end": 8.49, "char": [0, 2] },
        { "start": 8.49, "end": 10.986, "char": [3, 6] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 10.986,
      "end": 15.979,
      "text": "repository 推送到另一台机器两次。第一次推送传输全部内容，第二次只传输变更的部分。注意看数字，push",
      "words": [
        { "start": 10.986, "end": 13.483, "char": [0, 10] },
        { "start": 13.483, "end": 15.979, "char": [11, 56] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 15.979,
      "end": 18.476,
      "text": "命令会精确显示传输了多少数据。",
      "words": [{ "start": 15.979, "end": 18.476, "char": [0, 15] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 19.261,
      "end": 25.112,
      "text": "诀窍在于初始设置。第一次推送之后，CLI",
      "words": [{ "start": 19.261, "end": 25.112, "char": [0, 20] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 25.112,
      "end": 30.964,
      "text": "会在两台机器上各保留一份相同的不可变基础镜像。下一次推送时，系统将块与该基础镜像进行比较，只发送差异部分。不需要任何标志，不需要任何记录，用的就是同一个",
      "words": [{ "start": 25.112, "end": 30.964, "char": [0, 76] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 30.964,
      "end": 36.815,
      "text": "push",
      "words": [{ "start": 30.964, "end": 36.815, "char": [0, 4] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 36.815,
      "end": 42.667,
      "text": "命令。",
      "words": [{ "start": 36.815, "end": 42.667, "char": [0, 3] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 45.943,
      "end": 50.114,
      "text": "第一次推送到另一台机器会传输完整镜像，输出结果写得很清楚：传输了两",
      "words": [{ "start": 45.943, "end": 50.114, "char": [0, 33] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 50.114,
      "end": 54.285,
      "text": "GB，标记为",
      "words": [{ "start": 50.114, "end": 54.285, "char": [0, 6] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 54.285,
      "end": 58.456,
      "text": "full。这就是基准线。",
      "words": [{ "start": 54.285, "end": 58.456, "char": [0, 12] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 61.456,
      "end": 65.949,
      "text": "四十四秒传输两 GB，标记为",
      "words": [
        { "start": 61.456, "end": 63.702, "char": [0, 7] },
        { "start": 63.702, "end": 65.949, "char": [8, 14] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 65.949,
      "end": 70.442,
      "text": "full。CLI 同时在两端保留了相同的基础镜像，这就是后续魔法的前提。",
      "words": [
        { "start": 65.949, "end": 68.195, "char": [0, 8] },
        { "start": 68.195, "end": 70.442, "char": [9, 36] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 73.762,
      "end": 76.379,
      "text": "修改少量数据：两 GB 中的",
      "words": [
        { "start": 73.762, "end": 74.634, "char": [0, 8] },
        { "start": 74.634, "end": 75.507, "char": [9, 11] },
        { "start": 75.507, "end": 76.379, "char": [12, 14] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 76.379,
      "end": 78.124,
      "text": "50 MB。",
      "words": [
        { "start": 76.379, "end": 77.252, "char": [0, 2] },
        { "start": 77.252, "end": 78.124, "char": [3, 6] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 84.987,
      "end": 87.025,
      "text": "大镜像中的一点小改动。",
      "words": [{ "start": 84.987, "end": 87.025, "char": [0, 11] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 90.305,
      "end": 93.79,
      "text": "再次推送。命令一模一样，但这次看看输出：约 50",
      "words": [
        { "start": 90.305, "end": 92.048, "char": [0, 21] },
        { "start": 92.048, "end": 93.79, "char": [22, 24] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 93.79,
      "end": 97.276,
      "text": "MB 已传输，标记为",
      "words": [
        { "start": 93.79, "end": 95.533, "char": [0, 2] },
        { "start": 95.533, "end": 97.276, "char": [3, 10] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 97.276,
      "end": 100.761,
      "text": "delta，对比的是两 GB",
      "words": [
        { "start": 97.276, "end": 99.019, "char": [0, 11] },
        { "start": 99.019, "end": 100.761, "char": [12, 14] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 100.761,
      "end": 102.504,
      "text": "的镜像。只有发生变化的块被传输了。",
      "words": [{ "start": 100.761, "end": 102.504, "char": [0, 17] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 105.504,
      "end": 108.843,
      "text": "两 GB 的镜像，50",
      "words": [
        { "start": 105.504, "end": 106.617, "char": [0, 1] },
        { "start": 106.617, "end": 107.73, "char": [2, 4] },
        { "start": 107.73, "end": 108.843, "char": [5, 11] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 108.843,
      "end": 111.068,
      "text": "MB 在不到六秒内传输完毕。数字就是证明。",
      "words": [
        { "start": 108.843, "end": 109.955, "char": [0, 2] },
        { "start": 109.955, "end": 111.068, "char": [3, 21] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "start": 114.354,
      "end": 120.454,
      "text": "两台机器都保有相同的",
      "words": [{ "start": 114.354, "end": 120.454, "char": [0, 10] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 120.454,
      "end": 126.553,
      "text": "repository，几秒内完成同步。如果你愿意，每小时运行一次也没问题，费用取决于变更量，而不是总大小。",
      "words": [{ "start": 120.454, "end": 126.553, "char": [0, 53] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 129.553,
      "end": 131.591,
      "text": "频繁备份不再昂贵。",
      "words": [{ "start": 129.553, "end": 131.591, "char": [0, 9] }]
    },
    {
      "start": 132.43,
      "end": 142.539,
      "text": "第一次之后，每次小改动都意味着小传输。现在只剩最后一个教程了：确保你永远不会耗尽磁盘空间。最后一期见！",
      "words": [{ "start": 132.43, "end": 142.539, "char": [0, 51] }]
    }
  ]
}
